data.description: 13+/- Unrestricted Acres....nestled in the picturesque landscape of Floresville, Texas, this ranch property is a haven for those seeking the perfect blend of land and equestrian amenities. With a prime location in the heart of Texas ranch country, this property offers an incredible opportunity for land and ranch enthusiasts. The centerpiece of this ranch is its well-maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, providing a comfortable and welcoming living space. Whether you're an experienced equestrian or a horse enthusiast, you'll appreciate the dedicated horse barn and arena. These facilities are thoughtfully designed to cater to your needs, making this property ideal for horse lovers and ranchers alike. The sprawling 13+/- acres of land provide ample space for your vision, whether it's for building your dream home, recreational activities, cattle grazing, or expanding the equestrian facilities. Surrounded by the natural beauty of Texas, this property offers a serene and private retreat. Don't miss the opportunity to make this ranch property your own and experience the quintessential Texas lifestyle.
